      "comment": "BOSSALINI (2) is a two-year-old filly from the Courtney Laker stable on debut. Has the benefit of a good draw and will be ready to run a big race. MUDDY (7) is at the track for the first time. By Poster Boy and hails from the Mick Carbone stable. Will need a bit of luck negotiating a very wide starting position. Finds a nice race so anticipating a bright start to his career. LATHER IN GOLD (4) is on the radar after her last-start sixth over 2190m at Maryborough a month ago. Has race experience over a few of these and must be included. SPECIALS POSTER (6) is worth some thought after his last-start fifth over 1609m at Menangle on June 13. This is an easier task.",
